title: Inventory
episode_desc: Vaibhav migrates to Kota to prepare for India's toughest college entrance examination. Does this late entrant stand a chance in the race?
show_desc: Dedicated to Shrimati SL Loney ji, Shri Irodov ji and Maanniya HC Verma ji, 'Kota Factory' is TVF's latest original. India's first 'Black and White' show highlights the problems present day IIT-JEE aspirants face in their day-to-day lives.
